00:23:35.790 --> 00:23:38.210
mati betul-betul di hadapan saya, melampaui semua penyelamatan.

00:23:38.270 --> 00:23:39.250
Sekarang tiada apa-apa lagi

00:23:39.270 --> 00:23:40.730
